	<div class="getinvolved-title">
	<h2>Get Involved: Help Us Protect Clayoquot Sound</h2>
	</div>
	<h3>People power works!</h3>
	<p><p>Friends of Clayoquot Sound has proven that people power works—time and time again. Governments remember the massive protests that happened here in 1993, and they sit up and listen when people write in about Clayoquot. We’ve made it easy for you to do just that. Please add your voice now and be part of saving Clayoquot Sound for future generations.</p>
</p>
